queryLines:
SELECT 
    cust.marital_status,
    cust.Gender,
    cust.Country,
    fact.Sales,
    fact.Order_Number,
    fact.Order_Date,
    fact.due_date,
    fact.ship_date,
    prod.Category_Name,
    prod.Sub_Category_Name,
    prod.Product_Line,
    prod.Product_name
 FROM bara_slaes_project.gold.factable AS fact 
LEFT JOIN bara_slaes_project.gold.dimcustomer_infO AS cust
ON fact.Customer_ID=cust.Customer_ID
LEFT JOIN bara_slaes_project.gold.dimproduct_info AS prod
ON fact.Product_ID=prod.Product_ID;
